  "detailed_description": "A hilarious, weird and fun metroidvania with silly interactive cut scenes that force you to think outside the box!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/e155d977fc78e2a5fdf2895cd3e929a7.poster.avif?t=1772424181\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/e155d977fc78e2a5fdf2895cd3e929a7.webm?t=1772424181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/e155d977fc78e2a5fdf2895cd3e929a7.mp4?t=1772424181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The EVIL Pallid has stolen your gold! Shoot, Jet Pack and Bird? your way across colourful and dangerous worlds to stop his evil plan and get revenge!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/7a0db8afa0209168a2cab1df1113b19a.poster.avif?t=1772424181\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/7a0db8afa0209168a2cab1df1113b19a.webm?t=1772424181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/7a0db8afa0209168a2cab1df1113b19a.mp4?t=1772424181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Battle 8 Peculiar Bosses! Spoilers: It's Megasluggy, Pooch the Furry, Levaduck, Princess Obly, The Obapreed Brain, Evil Santa and Pallid himself, The villainous spook. Not to mention the secret boss!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/19540342ed6bb7db32988556e01df44f.poster.avif?t=1772424181\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/19540342ed6bb7db32988556e01df44f.webm?t=1772424181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/19540342ed6bb7db32988556e01df44f.mp4?t=1772424181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get Upto 14 Achievements such as speed-running the game in 60 minutes, beating the game on Impossible Mode or killing \"Mr Falco\" at the office!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/ab5f30f8c9a72855ebaa9616ae2cb656.poster.avif?t=1772424181\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/ab5f30f8c9a72855ebaa9616ae2cb656.webm?t=1772424181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126620/extras/ab5f30f8c9a72855ebaa9616ae2cb656.mp4?t=1772424181\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >credits</h2>Studio DynoStorm | Games (C) 2022 Super DynoStory - All Rights Reserved<br>Featuring the voices of PallidCrest as Pallid and Yoloswagstudios as Pooch.",
